dct_description_sm: Version. Internationall Institute for Geo-Information Science and Earth Observation (ITC) Relief shown by contour interval and spot heights. Relief representation is derived from elevation data of Shuttle Radar Topographic Mission (SRTM). Ground resolution 90 meters. Contour lines and drainage network are derived from the same elevation data. Topographic elements were supplied by the Department of Land Records. Ministry of Agriculture, Bhutan.
dct_publisher_sm: Thimpu : Bhutan. Ministry of Agriculture. Department of Surveys & Land Records, 2006.
